  "texts": [
    "A list of valid user agents used by plugins is maintained regularly in order to mask the malicious component of the web server.Figure 2 depicts the study trends on the use of LLMs in cyberattacks, and Table 2 provides a summary of the categorization.",
    "Figure 2 illustrates that initial access, defense evasion, and execution tactics are the primary points of concentration for the majority of attack methodologies.",
    "As a result, cybersecurity professionals must to give priority to these crucial phases while developing strategic protection methods against LLM-based attacks.In this paper, we reviewed the state-of-the-art research in the applications of Large Language Models (LLMs) within the realm of cybersecurity.",
    "We demonstrated that while LLMs can provide effective solutions for strengthening defensive approaches, their potential misuse cannot be underestimated.",
    "Hence, we categorized related literature using the NIST cybersecurity framework and MITRE attack for applications of LLMs in cyberdefense and cyberattacks, respectively."
  ]
}